  "Description": {
    "English": "Shifting nanite clusters sewn together with a <span class=\"name name-special\">pugneum filament</span>, this circuit is painfully hot to the touch. A sinister purple light leaks from deep within its wiring, changing in intensity as it watches its holder.<br><br>Unlike most Walker brains, this one has survived its violent extraction and is <span class=\"name name-technology\">pristine</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">undamaged</span>. It could potentially be installed in a new vessel...",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这块电路是通过<span class=\"name name-special\">普茵单纤维</span>连接的纳米星团，摸上去很烫手。线路深处漏出的邪恶紫光注视着持有者，并不断改变强度。<br><br>与绝大多数步行机的脑部不同，这块构件在经历了暴力性抽取手段后依旧<span class=\"name name-technology\">完好</span><span class=\"name name-technology\">无损</span>。也许能够用于安装在新装置里面......",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這塊電路板用<span class=\"name name-special\">搏絲</span>將會變形的奈米機群縫在一起，非常燙且難以觸碰。從線路深處洩出邪惡的紫色燈光，映照持有者時會改變閃爍頻率。<br><br>和大部分的步行機腦不同，這個腦從暴力抽取中倖存了下來，<span class=\"name name-technology\">完好無缺</span>且<span class=\"name name-technology\">未受損</span>。也許能夠安裝在新的容器中......"
  },
